result.notes: Survey of dogwhelks at 20 sites around Sullom Voe and Yell Sound, to study the incidence of imposex and its effects on population structure. Population data collected on site and dogwhelks sampled for imposex analysis at Marine Scotland Lab, Aberdeen.
